%% Reflects ADR-001: this diagram is repurposed from the old "blacklist on
%% rotation" flow. Rotation itself is now shown inline in GF-03 (delete +
%% insert on refresh). This diagram covers the other revocation trigger:
%% explicit logout. No Redis is involved — DB deletion is the revocation.
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Gateway
    participant ServiceAuth
    participant DB

    User            ->>  Gateway        :   HTTP POST http://server-gateway/logout <br/>(with Refresh Token)
    Gateway         ->>  ServiceAuth    :   HTTP POST http://service-auth/api/v1/auth/logout <br/>LogoutRequest
    ServiceAuth     ->>  DB             :   DELETE FROM refresh_token WHERE token = ?
    DB              -->> ServiceAuth    :   ok (idempotent — no error if already deleted)
    ServiceAuth     -->> Gateway        :   HTTP 200 OK
    Gateway         -->> User           :   HTTP 200 OK
